title: The Wedding Photos
description:
Hey, did we ever show you guys our wedding photos?

Starring Dan Hodapp, Langan Kingsley, Lisa Kleinman, and Jonathan Marballi
Written by Jess Dweck
Directed by Jim Santangeli
Shot and Edited by Alex Adan

Taped on January 30th, 2012
